<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>هـ ف ف<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٥٤٢٧ - هـ ف ف]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>هَفَّ هَفَفْتُ، يَهِفّ، اهْفِفْ/ هِفّ، هَفًّا وهفيفًا، فهو<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>⦗٢٣٥٥⦘ هافّ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• هفََّت الرّيحُ:</span> هبَّت فسُمِعَ صوت هبوبها.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">• هفَّ الشَّخصُ:</span> أسرع في سيره ° هفَّت نفسُه.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">• هفَّ الحِمْلُ:</span> خَفَّ وزنُه.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">• هفَّ الزَّرعُ:</span> انتشر حَبُّه لتأخُّر حصاده.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>